This paper is likely to belong to the category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) as it deals with improving Neural Machine Translation (NMT) using data selection techniques. It could also belong to the category of Machine Learning (cs.LG) as it involves training NMT models. Additionally, it could be categorized under Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) as NMT is a subfield of AI. Neural Networks (cs.NE) and Computer Vision (cs.CV) could also be possible categories as they are related to NMT.
